{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act35side", "eventName": "太陽甩在身後", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AS-ST-3", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "十字路口，再出發", "storyInfo": "劫後餘生的眾人相互告別，紛紛踏上了新的旅途。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$comedy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g10_grandbazaar_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真可惜，我的庭院只被毀了一半。我還想借此機會幫庭院換個風貌，結果剩下的雕塑和植物反而不方便處理。", "name": "珠光寶氣的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過修復工作倒是差不多完成了，也許休息日你有興趣來坐坐？", "name": "珠光寶氣的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多謝好意，恐怕我抽不開身。我的寶石收藏都混到了一起，為了恢復那間幾百年的收藏室，我需要先逐一鑑定石頭的功效。", "name": "衣著考究的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，博物館損壞的事情……", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_emoji_proud", "layer": 1.0, "y": 180.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#6$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我絕對會瞞過去的！要是瞞不過去，我就對父親曉之以理，動之以情……總之，他會幫忙說服所有投資者的。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#6$3"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有博物館那批特殊的新藏品。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$2"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#6$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，這個我也會在信裡幫你們說清楚的。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#6$3"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我不覺得父親會同意你們對所有人展出寶石構裝體重建的古建築局部喔？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我理解，比起展示，博物館更重要的工作是保存歷史……也包括保持歷史的背面不被人看見。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，佩佩，我今晚可以睡個好覺了。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#14$2"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對不對，不是我該對你們道謝嗎？感謝你和緹緹幫我尋找寶石，完成了這次歷史大發現，以及……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……娜仁圖亞小姐？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯？沒事沒事，就是聽你們講了半天博物館的事有點無聊。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我把您請過來，原本是想和佩佩一起，向您表達感謝……", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_emoji_blackline", "layer": 1.0, "x": 50.0, "y": 180.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#11$2"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜仁圖亞女士，您說希望把“優待阿雅吉和阿雅妮”寫進館規，我們正在……以一種比較隱晦的方式兌現。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#11$2"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$3"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是哪個時代的陶俑嗎？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$3"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，是博物館兩名正式入職的新人。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算天氣熱得路都熔化了，也會按時去上班的兩個傻子。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在卸下代理館長的職責，離開博物館之前，我會交代大家特別關照她們的。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$3"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我還是很難相信，阿娜特。你真的要放棄現在的職位嗎？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$3"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#11$2"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，父親不會喜歡我這個決定的。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#11$2"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我從記事起就一直透過窗戶看著這座城市，現在我覺得，或許我已經把它讀完了。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它的歷史，它的前身。它深埋地下的、若沒有你這樣橫衝直撞的探險者就不會被發掘的祕密。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "53_i12", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真奇妙，只過了兩天，城市就恢復運轉了。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然那麼多房子不知道要修補到什麼時候，出現裂痕的路也要重新鋪……但是水道已經完全清澈了。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那當然啦。河水是一直在流淌的嘛。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是呀，河水永遠向前流淌，無論多少座城市變成沙子，沙子上再建起多少座城市。", "name": "佩佩"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……讓流水帶走一切，或許算不上一種選擇，只是在永恆面前這是必然的結果。", "name": "佩佩"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但永恆本無意義。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，就像緹緹說的那樣，博物館偶爾辦一些特別的展覽，其實也不壞。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼哼，這個我也覺得。", "name": "佩佩"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，我來到這裡之前，還真的幻想過一場驚心動魄的冒險。", "name": "佩佩"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我想的可不是現在這種，而是有人盯上了我的寶石，我要跟他鬥智鬥勇。", "name": "佩佩"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，實際上根本沒人跟我作對，想想還有點可惜呢。", "name": "佩佩"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈哈。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g17_deserttown_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$2", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，佩佩，我還有一個問題想向你請教。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$2"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道的，我一直都很崇拜埃里克森先生。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$2"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然我之前研究祖拜爾的論文已經全數作廢……我希望像埃里克森先生一樣，去看看大地上其他的地方。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，像他一樣將自己的見聞整理成信……再寄給他！", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#7$2"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，我一定要和他成為筆友！", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#7$2"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，這倒是離開博物館的充分理由。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是你站在城市街心花園裡都能中暑，要去野外考察，至少也該先找個力士訓練體能吧？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$3"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我才要向你學習經驗，佩佩。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$2"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#12$2"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我可以坐著有冷氣的長途車走遍大地嗎？", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#12$2"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g6_museum_core", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "cgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_41_i12_1", "style": "cg", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1484_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-50"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.8, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_signalInterference", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_oldtv", "layer": 3.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "timersticker", "attributes": {"x": 935.0, "y": 80.0, "width": 300.0, "size": 45.0, "time": 9999.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "o"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1484_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對不起，娜仁圖亞，我們也想送得更遠一點。", "name": "阿雅吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是為了全勤獎，我們必須在博物館努力工作。", "name": "阿雅吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1484_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且這個攝影機真的很好玩——", "name": "阿雅吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1484_1#11$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#8$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "-30,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "jump", "posto": "-50,0", "power": 2.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴，這是要送給娜仁圖亞的錄影帶，她會一直帶在身邊的。", "name": "阿雅妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1485_1#8$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，娜仁圖亞，特別特別想你的時候，我們會往河裡丟金幣的。", "name": "阿雅妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1485_1#9$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1485_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說城裡那條河會一直流到大地的盡頭，所以你無論去了哪裡，一定能撿到我們留下的金幣。", "name": "阿雅妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1485_1#10$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1484_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，阿雅妮說得對。", "name": "阿雅吉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1484_1#12$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "o", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "timerclear", "attributes": {"afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "hidecgitem", "attributes": {"image": "cgitem_41_i12_1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g1_menatmainstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$memory_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要指出一個地理學上的事實，實際上這條河甚至不會流到米諾斯。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些事情你可以不說出口。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說，我也不打算走到大地盡頭。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#3$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……為什麼突然決定丟下她們，一個人去走“天途”？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可沒丟下她們，只是那兩個最傻的小孩終於也找到去處了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天途的規矩，以前我是一條都做不到，現在我至少可以一個人到處走走，順便給這段旅途取個名字叫天途。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不是很省事嗎？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾幾次在心裡猜測你是不是夢魘，但我以為你避諱自己這一身分。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？只是沒什麼好說的，所以沒說。要是我娜仁圖亞的名字不能比夢魘這個身分更響亮，那多丟臉啊。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那你天途的終點在哪裡？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按道理來說，天途最後應該走回自己家，但我很早以前犯了一些事，所以回不去了……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#4$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，雖然大家一般把自己選擇的試煉之地稱作終點，但天途得到了試煉之地再活著回家，才算結束。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，那才是最難的。很多人都會越走越遠。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不喜歡為難自己，不如……等我收到下一個手下，就算天途結束吧。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#5$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……祝願你路途順利。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢？這幾天在博物館裡參觀夠了？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅捷緹克緹女士的慷慨使我得以瀏覽諸多非公開藏品，但所見越多，我越能察覺我知識的空缺，乃至米諾斯歷史的空白。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#2$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在幫助她們寫完改建米諾斯展廳的文書之後，我在這裡已經沒有更多能做的事情。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#2$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會帶著這些館藏的照片回米諾斯，將資料提交給專家，希望他們能證明米諾斯曾有哲學辯論這一項競技。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……然後，或許我會帶著金杯回家看看。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，說到這個，我還有件禮物要給你。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長途車隊快出發了，你趕快拿著它逃……不是，拿著它回米諾斯吧。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再會了，朋友。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "背過夕陽，娜仁圖亞瀟灑地轉過身，邁開步子。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不出所料，片刻之後，身後傳來了阿斯帕齊婭驚訝的聲音。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "53_i13_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是存放在博物館裡的那個金——", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只要說聲謝謝，然後帶著贓物火速離開就好。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別多問。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝謝。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈，你竟然真的不問？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些事情我可以不說出口。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "衷心感謝你，娜仁圖亞，這趟旅途我收穫頗豐。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啊。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車隊將要出發的搖鈴聲響起，娜仁圖亞頭也不回地擺了擺手。"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有我給的金子作為祝福，你最好能拿到一塊金牌。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "53_i13_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到收穫……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忙碌了一個月，弄到手的唯一一件寶物就是那個金杯……好像還有什麼呢，算了，想不起來了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒關係，這都是我自己選的。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金子作的一個杯子嘛，以後一定還會有的！", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g12_gemexchange", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉恕爾啊，你都要走了，真的不能讓我表演一次嗎？", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#2$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我保證會把你的發條小玩具一口吞掉，再完整地吐出來，不留任何牙印。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#2$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……如果你真的想，我又能拿你有什麼辦法呢？", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#2$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吞吧。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想知道，它還能不能脫胎換骨，長出真正的羽毛。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "牠只是捨不得你，拉恕爾。你不用被牠拖延腳步。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寶石交易所立下的規則已經深入人心，沒有你，大巴扎也會推選出新的監管人，或者制定另一種秩序。你盡可以放心地離開。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你們的存在近乎永恆，真的還會感到不捨嗎？", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#3$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，這可是輝煌之城的寶石交易所，我從來都是挑最好的住處！", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#2$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以試試去養一隻真正的寵物。不是我與米奧這樣的獸主，也不是發條羽獸。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#5$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據我觀察，成功的商人都會飼養很特別的寵物，所以你至少要以白化羽獸或者三公尺長的彩色鱗為標準，明白嗎？", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#5$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來吧，摸摸頭。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#5$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cakebgflgrnd", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#7$1", "duration": 0.2}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "jump", "posto": "200,150", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "power": 20.0, "times": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#6$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meowlong", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米奧看似並不情願地跳到人類面前的方桌上，低下頭，盤起尾巴。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#8$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_catgrunting", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（呼嚕聲）", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#8$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_closeeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g16_desertoasis", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#8$1", "posfrom": "100,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#8$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g13_invertedpyramid", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見，小人類。", "name": "米奧"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g12_gemexchange", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見。", "name": "米奧"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g12_gemexchange", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "許久之後，牠睜開眼睛。無人注目的房間裡，牠身後的影子變得龐大，遠超一隻雲獸的體型。"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那麼，你還要留在這裡嗎？", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祖拜爾已經安息並離開，沙阿的後人取得了寶庫的真相，那些在漫長時光中迴響的囈語……", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，你也把夢魘帶去看那些金銀珠寶了，對吧？", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她跳進地下水道深處，已經證明了自己的勇氣，所以，我履行了對祖拜爾的承諾。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "承諾……祖拜爾離開之後，我們的承諾也算是全部完成了吧。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的，千年之前的，都完成了。這座城市已經和我們最初的承諾沒有任何關係了。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我還是會留下來，因為現在這座城市活著。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我承諾守護死者，是為了他們的復生。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為你會懷念黃金之城。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今那座沉默的黃金之城嗎？它已經不需要我們了。", "name": "沃奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，是啊，一整座城市都像被萬王之王割掉了舌頭，我不喜歡。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我和你的想法不一樣。我偏要去看看。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#4$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g6_museum_core", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，把需要拜訪的投資者名單給我吧。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這邊的藏品你們清點一下，後續我來安排修復工作。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……等等，這個不是琥珀，不要送到自然類展區。你沒看到裡面是一塊寶石構裝體的殘片嗎？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#8$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個你就當是我的私人藏品，先放在一邊……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#8$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pawfootstep_3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#6$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meowlong", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——好眼熟的雲獸，是拉恕爾家的那隻嗎？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-50,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，讓我摸摸你的毛，看看你這次嘴裡會吐出來什麼……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，嗯，對，這正是我想要的。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#2$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_meownormal", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，是我在說話。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在你已經被我指定為飼養員，明白了嗎？", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之後要去哪裡，你就得聽我的了。", "name": "米奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}, {"id": 410, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "半年後", "duration": 1.0, "x": 300.0, "y": 325.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 26.0, "delay": 0.0, "width": 700.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g8_sargondeluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩佩，有人找你。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍等……我還有一句結語就要完成了。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和你關於祖拜爾的論文吸引了不少學術界人士與媒體，這幾天要前來拜訪你的人絡繹不絕。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你覺得困擾，我可以為你回絕。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沒關係，我都可以見見。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我希望這篇論文能吸引到更多的人，這些關於祖拜爾的文字，我希望能受到全薩爾貢的關注。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那好，我帶她進來了。", "name": "阿娜特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 446, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1487_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，您的步態很是輕盈，一路走來，我只聽到您身上的配飾響動，卻絲毫聽不到您的腳步聲。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1487_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔……輝煌的史官家族……不被選擇的繼承者……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1487_1#7$1"}, {"id": 455, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是……？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 457, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1487_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我忘了介紹一下自己。我是萬王之王的使者……", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1487_1#10$1"}, {"id": 459, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1487_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想為陛下向您轉達感激與讚賞，感激您為薩爾貢歷史所添下的精彩一筆，還有，我要給您一道陛下親授的旨意。", "name": "來自黃金之城的使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 461, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 463, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1487_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈特謝普蘇特，陛下希望您親臨黃金之城，為他講述您在米納特哈瑪儀的經歷。", "name": "來自黃金之城的使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1487_1#1$1"}, {"id": 465, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1487_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煩請開始為動身做準備吧，陛下正期待著您的到來。", "name": "來自黃金之城的使者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1487_1#7$1"}, {"id": 467, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}